; https://github.com/tldr-pages/tldr/blob/master/pages/common/zeroclaw-migrate.md

% zeroclaw-migrate, common

# Preview migration from OpenClaw without writing data
zeroclaw migrate openclaw --dry-run

# Migrate memory from OpenClaw workspace
zeroclaw migrate openclaw

# Display help
zeroclaw migrate <__h___help_>
